                        <i class="fas fa-clock"></i>
                    </div>
                    <h3>Flexible Time</h3>
                    <p>Work at your own pace, anytime, anywhere. Perfect for students and part-time workers</p>
                </div>
                
                <div class="benefit-card">
                    <div class="benefit-icon">
                        <i class="fas fa-users"></i>
                    </div>
                    <h3>Referral Bonus</h3>
                    <p>Earn Ksh 50 for every friend you refer who joins and activates their account</p>
                </div>
                
                <div class="benefit-card">
                    <div class="benefit-icon">
                        <i class="fas fa-mobile-alt"></i>
                    </div>
                    <h3>M-Pesa Payments</h3>
                    <p>Get paid directly to your M-Pesa account. Minimum withdrawal is just Ksh 500</p>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </section>

    <!-- FAQ Section -->
    <section class="faq-section">
        <div class="container">
            <h2 class="text-center mb-3">Frequently Asked Questions</h2>
            <div class="faq-grid">
                <div class="faq-item">
                    <h3>Why do I need to pay Ksh 400?</h3>
                    <p>The registration fee helps us maintain the platform, verify accounts, and ensure quality tasks. It's a one-time payment that activates your earning potential.</p>
                </div>
                
                <div class="faq-item">
                    <h3>How much can I earn?</h3>
                    <p>You can earn Ksh 20-500 per task depending on the complexity. Active members typically earn Ksh 5,000-15,000 per month.</p>
                </div>
                
                <div class="faq-item">
                    <h3>How do I get paid?</h3>
                    <p>Payments are made directly to your M-Pesa account. You can withdraw your earnings once you reach the minimum threshold of Ksh 500.</p>
                </div>
                
                <div class="faq-item">
                    <h3>Is this legitimate?</h3>
                    <p>Yes! PAPKASH is a registered company in Kenya. We have paid out over Ksh 50,000 to our members and continue to grow.</p>
                </div>
